        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer46135570" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6918808975935030745">I have now finished the entire series and loved all of the books. The parts I liked the most was the historical detail on the war. I learned alot from the descriptions of what each character went through in the war. I really felt like I was there. The other part I liked was that each of the characters were fully developed and I saw myself in some of them or I saw people I knew. I could really relate to their personalities. Great series, I highly recommend.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


