<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23605373-a-generation-rising"><img alt="A Generation Rising (Fire and Steel #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1418970276l/23605373._SX98_.jpg" />
